### Query camera recordings
POST http://localhost:5226/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Was there any movement detected recently?"
}

### Query about specific objects
POST http://localhost:5226/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Were there any animals in the camera recordings?"
}

### Query about specific time
POST http://localhost:5226/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What happened in the last hour?"
}